name: 丹尼斯·丹尼尔
name_full: 丹尼斯·丹尼尔 Dennis Daniel
introduction: Also known as mobile pro DJ Doublevision LLC became a DJ in the 2000's. He also did b boy dancing and singing. Presently he hosts and produces his own local cable TV show on HC Media in Haverhill Massachusetts, giving a platform to entertainers and musicians alike. Coming from downtown Brooklyn, NY, he has always wanted to be an actor. Slowly moved to New Jersey, spent some time in Pennsylvania, and ended up in the suburbs of Boston. Dennis eventually got involved in DJ and acting. Continuing to hone his craft at Northern Essex Community College with acting classes, he is striving to perfect his onscreen abilities. He was lucky enough to be a member of the Oscar and Sundance award winning cast of CODA. A Show Stopping Christmas is also one of his proudest bodies of work to date.A hard worker is all he is ever known to do.Part of this great actor is his Latin roots .
